    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、こころちゃん？\n話があるなら、お部屋でも良かったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ Kokoro-chan?\nIf you wanted to say something‚ you could've told me in your room‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.2333338618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、これは秘密の話ですから\n琴乃ちゃんのお誕生日企画の話、どう思いました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ this is a secret!\nWhat did you think about the birthday project for Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.1333338618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "面白そうだな～って思ったよ？　三人でプレゼントを\n選びに行って、当日みんなにサプライズで渡すんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it sounded fun? The three of us will go pick out presents‚\nand then surprise everyone with them on her birthday‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.6333338618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、シンプルで分かりやすくて、いいと思います\nでも、ひと手間加えれば、さらに盛り上がるかな～って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it’s simple and straightforward‚ I think it’s good.\nHowever‚ if we add a little something extra‚ it could be even funnier~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.3666671951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "そこで考えました。プレゼントを配る琴乃ちゃんに\n逆にプレゼントをあげちゃえばいいんじゃないかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I thought! Why don’t we give a present to Kotono-chan‚\nwho’s giving everyone presents?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.6000005285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "名付けて、逆ドッキリならぬ、逆プレゼント大作戦！\n二人でこっそり準備して、驚かせちゃいませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I call it‚ not a reverse prank‚ but a Reverse Present Operation!\nWe can secretly prepare something and surprise her!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.4333399653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんにプレゼントか～\nお誕生日だし、そういうのがあってもいいかもね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A present for Kotono-chan…\nIt might be a good idea since it’s her birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.300006632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
