      "text": "企画も絶対盛り上がると思うんですよ～\n内緒のプレゼントに驚く琴乃ちゃん、その瞳には涙が！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure the project will be so much fun~!\nKotono-chan will be surprised by the secret present‚ and her eyes will well up with tears!",
        "id": ""
