      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、こころちゃん、優しいね\n琴乃ちゃんのために考えてあげたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ Kokoro-chan‚ you’re so kind.\nYou came up with that for Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
